		"description": "Complete API collection for QueueMaster - A hybrid queue and appointment management system.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n1. Set collection variables:\n   - `base_url`: http://127.0.0.1:8080\n   - `access_token`: (will be set automatically after login)\n\n2. Start with Auth > Login to get your access token\n3. The token will be automatically saved to the collection variable\n4. All authenticated requests will use this token automatically\n\n## Test Users (if using seed data)\n\n- **Admin:** admin@example.com / password123\n- **Attendant:** attendant@example.com / password123\n- **Client:** client@example.com / password123",
